### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱشْتَرَوُا۟ ٱلْكُفْرَ بِٱلْإِيمَـٰنِ لَن يَضُرُّوا۟ ٱللَّهَ شَيْـًٔا وَلَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ</span>

### English

Those who trade belief for disbelief will never harm Allah in the least, and they will suffer a painful punishment.